org.cyclops.integrateddynamics.core.block

Interface ICollidable<P>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - The type of positions this component type can provide.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlockCable, CollidableComponent

    public interface ICollidable<P>
    Interface for blocks that have a collidable component. Delegate calls to CollidableComponent.
